tutorial-closed-announcement: Kua katia te akoranga. Kia maumahara ka taea e koe te whakamahi i te Alt me te Shift me te A hei whakatuwhera me te kati i te rārangi whiringa urutau, Alt me te Shift me ngā pere hei whakatere i waenga i ngā whārangi, me te Alt me te Shift me te X hei whakatuwhera me te kati i te rārangi whakatere. Ka taea e koe te uru atu ki ngā mahi urutau anō mā te pātene i te kokonga matau.
tutorial-completed-announcement: Kua oti te akoranga. Kia maumahara ka taea e koe te whakamahi i te Alt me te Shift me te A hei whakatuwhera me te kati i te rārangi whiringa urutau, Alt me te Shift me ngā pere hei whakatere i waenga i ngā whārangi, me te Alt me te Shift me te X hei whakatuwhera me te kati i te rārangi whakatere.
tutorial-description-content:
I mua i tō tīmatanga, anei tētahi haerenga tere hei whakaatu ki a koe me pēhea te whakatere, te whakamahi i te rārangi me te uru atu ki ngā āhuatanga whaihua.
Kāore e roa!
tutorial-exit-button-aria-label: Katia te akoranga me te haere tonu ki te akoranga
tutorial-starting-announcement: E tīmata ana te akoranga. Te taahiraa tuatahi: me pēhea te whakamahi i te rārangi whakatere. Kia maumahara ka taea e koe te whakamahi i te Alt me te Shift me te Z hei whakatuwhera me te kati i te rārangi whakatere.
tutorial-step-1-content: Mā tēnei pātene ka taea e koe te uru ki ngā upoko me ngā mahi o te pukapuka.
tutorial-step-2-content: Whakamahia ngā pere hei whakatere i ngā whārangi rerekē o te pukapuka.
tutorial-step-3-content:
Ka taea e koe te whakahohe i ngā taputapu ako i konei pēnei i te:

🤓 pānui māmā
🔊 kuputuhi ki te reo
✋ reo tohu
🤖 whakamārama AI
🔤 papakupu
tutorial-welcome-announcement: Nau mai ki tēnei pukapuka i tōna hōputu urutau. Kei te wātea ngā pokatata papapātuhi: Alt me te Shift me ngā pere hei whakatere i waenga i ngā whārangi, Alt me te Shift me te A hei whakatuwhera me te kati i te rārangi whiringa urutau, Alt me te Shift me te X hei whakatuwhera me te kati i te whakatere. Mā tētahi akoranga poto koe e ārahi i ngā mahi e wātea ana.
tutorial-welcome-title: Nau mai ki te pukapuka matihiko urutau
validation-write-appropriate: Tēnā tuhia ki te reo tika me te whakamahi i te reo e tika ana
